#: .\Items\melee_tools.json
msgid "inactive BL9 Manhack MK i"
msgid_plural "inactive BL9 Manhack MK is"
msgstr[0] "未激活的BL9追猎者MK i型"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive BL9 Manhack MK i'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive BL9 Manhack MK ii'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive BL9 Manhack MK iii'}
#: .\Items\melee_tools.json
msgid ""
"An inactive BL9 manhack, a fist-sized BL9 controlled robot that increases "
"greatly in size when you launch it in the air. It's fast, it's damaging, but"
" it's not that tanky. It's capable of smashing enemies, doing ranged "
"attacks, shooting it's organic gun that can stun enemies. Each increasing "
"mark of BL9 manhacks becomes stronger, greater at protecting you. You still "
"need to reprogram and activate the manhack, though electronics and computer "
"skill requirements are much lower for these versions than for standard "
"industrial manhacks."
msgstr ""
"一个未激活的BL9追猎者，拳头大小、由BL9控制的机器人，当你将其发射到空中时会大幅增大体积。它速度快、伤害高，但不算特别耐打。它能粉碎敌人、进行远程攻击、发射可击晕敌人的有机枪械。BL9追猎者的每个更高型号都会变得更强，更能保护你。不过你仍需重新编程并激活追猎者，尽管这些版本对电子和计算机技能的要求远低于标准工业追猎者。"

