#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Herb Cleansing"
msgstr "草药净化"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Herb Cleansing'.
#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid ""
"You have taken some healing herb.  It appears to have panacea-like effects "
"along with radiation cleansing properties slowly cleansing your body of "
"radiation; if you take more of it, you'll be able to speed up the process."
msgstr "你服用了一些治疗草药。它似乎具有类似万灵药的效果，同时具备辐射净化特性，正缓慢清除你体内的辐射；若服用更多，将能加速此过程。"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Mild Herb Stun"
msgstr "轻度草药眩晕"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Moderate Herb Stun"
msgstr "中度草药眩晕"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Strong Herb Stun"
msgstr "强烈草药眩晕"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Powerful Herb Stun"
msgstr "强力草药眩晕"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Intense Herb Stun"
msgstr "剧烈草药眩晕"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid ""
"You have taken some healing herb.  It appears to have pretty strong "
"stunning, dizzying effects; these effects are temporary, but if you take "
"more of it right away, they will stack."
msgstr "你服用了一些治疗草药。它似乎具有相当强烈的眩晕和致晕效果；这些效果是暂时的，但如果你立即服用更多，它们会叠加。"

#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
msgid "Spray Cleansing"
msgstr "喷雾净化"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Spray Cleansing'.
#: .\Monsters\mon_effects.json
