"You have sprayed yourself with some healing spray.  It appears to have "
"panacea-like effects along with radiation cleansing properties slowly "
"cleansing your body of radiation; if you spray yourself more with it, you'll"
" be able to speed up the process."
msgstr "你对自己喷洒了一些治疗喷雾。它似乎具有类似万灵药的效果，同时具备辐射净化特性，能缓慢清除体内的辐射；如果你喷洒更多，可以加速这个过程。"

