msgstr "BL9力量强化"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Strengthening'}
#: .\Monsters\mon_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You feel a boost in strength (+3 str) while wearing this particular "
"artifact, it feels not as if you're controlled but guided by an entity or so"
" you think..."
msgstr "佩戴此特殊遗物时，你感到力量有所提升（+3力量），这种感觉并非像被控制，而是仿佛受到某个存在的引导，至少你是这么认为的……"

#: .\Monsters\mon_mutations.json
msgid "BL9 Endurance"
msgstr "BL9耐力提升"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 Endurance'}
#: .\Monsters\mon_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You feel that you can endure the hardships of Cataclysm better (+55% to "
"maximal carry weight, -25% to fatigue, slight protection from bleeding) "
"while wearing this particular artifact, it feels not as if you're controlled"
" but guided by an entity or so you think..."
msgstr ""
"佩戴此特殊遗物时，你感觉自己能更好地承受灾变的磨难（最大负重+55%，疲劳度-25%，轻微防流血效果），这种感觉并非像被控制，而是仿佛受到某个存在的引导，至少你是这么认为的……"

