#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid ""
"A BL9-induced human with it's head ruptured, revealing a large and slender "
"segmented worm-like parasite. With it's wide-gaping mouth, it can be deadly "
"when it comes to biting."
msgstr "一个受BL9影响的人类，其头部破裂，暴露出一个巨大而细长的分节蠕虫状寄生虫。凭借其大张的嘴，咬击时可能致命。"

