#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid ""
"A zealot in long red robes wearing a strange skull mask infused with the BL9"
" who carries a lot of coins. It appears to be sentient, having all "
"characteristics of a normal person except for strangely solemn gaze, "
"disturbingly pale skin and bloodshot eyes indicating the presence of "
"artificially modified BL9 to make them more violent, obedient,  their motive"
" is to kill those that didn't accept the blessing of their \"dios\", this "
"one is armed with a sword and it seems to know how to use it well."
msgstr ""
"一个身穿红色长袍、戴着奇怪骷髅面具、注入了BL9并携带大量硬币的狂热者。它似乎具有意识，拥有正常人的所有特征，除了异常严肃的目光、令人不安的苍白皮肤和布满血丝的眼睛，这表明存在人工改造的BL9，使其更具暴力性和服从性。他们的动机是杀死那些不接受其“神”祝福的人。这个邪教徒装备着一把剑，并且似乎很擅长使用它。"

