#. ~ Description for {'str': "Armed 'True Superiors' BL9-Mercenary - Rifle"}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid ""
"An armored professional mercenary infused with the BL9. It appears to be "
"sentient, having all characteristics of a normal person except for strangely"
" aggressive and bothered look on it's face, evidently faster reflexes and "
"bloodshot eyes indicating the presence of artificially modified BL9 to make "
"them more violent, obedient,  they will do their best to stop any intruder "
"that managed to infiltrate their compound, this one is armed with a rifle "
"and it obviously knows how to use it well."
msgstr ""
"一个注入了BL9的装甲职业雇佣兵。它似乎具有意识，拥有正常人的所有特征，除了脸上异常好斗和烦躁的表情、明显更快的反应速度以及布满血丝的眼睛，这表明存在人工改造的BL9，使其更具暴力性和服从性。他们会竭尽全力阻止任何成功潜入其设施的入侵者。这个雇佣兵装备着一把步枪，并且显然很擅长使用它。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid "The ganados fires it's rifle!"
msgstr "邪教徒发射了它的步枪！"

