#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid ""
"A BL9-induced human with it's head ruptured, protruding from it is a "
"parasite with several spindly spiky limbs and an acid-drooling "
"orifice.Multiple tentacles are growing out of the sides of it's body "
"swinging wildly in all directions."
msgstr ""
"一个由BL9诱发的人类，其头部破裂，从中突出一条寄生虫，该寄生虫有几条细长的尖刺肢体和一个流着酸液的口器。多根触手从它身体两侧长出，向各个方向疯狂摆动。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid "Armed BL9-Behemoth - Sledgehammer"
msgid_plural "Armed BL9-Behemoth - Sledgehammers"
msgstr[0] "武装的BL9巨兽 - 大锤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Armed BL9-Behemoth - Sledgehammer'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Armed Patrolling BL9-Behemoth - Sledgehammer'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid ""
"A heavily armored mercenary infused with the BL9. It seems to have grown in "
"size being over 7 feet tall.It appears to be sentient, having all "
"characteristics of a normal person except for strangely very aggressive look"
" on it's face, greater strength and endurance, bloodshot eyes indicating the"
" presence of artificially modified BL9 to make them more violent, obedient,"
"  they will do their best to stop any intruder that managed to infiltrate "
"their compound, this one is armed with a huge sledgehammer and it obviously "
"knows how to use it well."
msgstr ""
"一名注入了BL9的重装甲佣兵。它似乎体型增大，身高超过7英尺。它似乎具有意识，拥有正常人的所有特征，除了脸上奇怪地带着非常攻击性的表情，更强的力量和耐力，充血的眼睛表明存在人工改造的BL9，使其更加暴力、顺从，他们会竭尽全力阻止任何成功潜入他们设施的入侵者，这一个装备了一把巨大的大锤，并且显然很擅长使用它。"

