#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\Infantry.json
msgid ""
"An armored professional soldier with a very calculating look wearing a sleek"
" hi-tech combat suit infused with the BL9 who carries a lot of coins. It "
"appears to be sentient, having all characteristics of a normal person except"
" for strangely aggressive and bothered look on it's face, evidently faster "
"reflexes and bloodshot eyes indicating the presence of artificially modified"
" BL9 to make them more violent, obedient,  they will do their best to stop "
"any intruder that managed to infiltrate their compound, this one is armed "
"with an energy machine gun, pack of strange energy grenades and it obviously"
" knows how to use them well."
msgstr ""
"一名身着注入BL9的流线型高科技战斗服、眼神精于算计的装甲职业士兵，携带着大量硬币。它似乎具有意识，拥有正常人的所有特征，除了脸上异常好斗且烦躁的表情，明显更快的反应速度以及布满血丝的眼睛表明其体内存在人工改造的BL9，使其更具暴力性和服从性，它们会竭尽全力阻止任何成功潜入其设施的入侵者。此个体配备了一把能量机枪和一包奇特的能量手榴弹，显然精通使用它们。"

