#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid "Repto"
msgid_plural "Reptos"
msgstr[0] "爬行怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Repto'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid-reptilian hybrid with sharp, glistening claws. It's body "
"orientation is built for leaping, thus making it capable of lunging at "
"unsuspecting preys."
msgstr "一种人形与爬行类生物的混合体，拥有锋利闪亮的爪子。其身体结构专为跳跃而设计，因此能够扑向毫无防备的猎物。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid "Evolved Repto"
msgid_plural "Evolved Reptos"
msgstr[0] "进化爬行怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Evolved Repto'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid ""
"A modified version of the horrible reptilian mutant, they have a resilient "
"shell-like epidermis that grants them additional protection from small arms."
" The creatures' left arms are still slightly longer than their right, though"
" the claws on both are wickedly sharp. Both sides of it's mouth are flanked "
"by mandibles, giving them a more unsettling appearance"
msgstr ""
"这种可怕爬行类突变体的改良版本，拥有坚韧的壳状表皮，为它们提供了额外的轻武器防护。这些生物的左手仍略长于右手，但双爪都异常锋利。其嘴部两侧生有颚肢，使它们的外表更加令人不安。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid "Shadow Crawler"
msgid_plural "Shadow Crawlers"
msgstr[0] "暗影爬行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Crawler'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid ""
"A winged bug-like creature that hovers mid-air. It has a pair of razor-sharp"
" claws and a head similar to cockcroaches."
msgstr "一种能够在半空中悬浮的有翼虫类生物。它拥有一对锋利的爪子和一个类似蟑螂的头部。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid "Evolved Shadow Crawler"
msgid_plural "Evolved Shadow Crawlers"
msgstr[0] "进化暗影爬行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Evolved Shadow Crawler'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid ""
"A bug-like bipedal creature with a set of serrated chitin blades on it's "
"forelimbs. It has thick formation of chitin shelling that protects it from "
"harm."
msgstr "一种双足虫类生物，其前肢长有一组锯齿状的几丁质刀刃。它拥有厚重的几丁质外壳，能保护其免受伤害。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid "BL9 ivy zombie"
msgid_plural "BL9 ivy zombies"
msgstr[0] "BL9常春藤僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 ivy zombie'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid ""
"A corpse severely infested by the plant of unknown variety. Although it's "
"movement is very stiff, it's mouth has altered to an extent, it occupies the"
" entirety of it's face that's lined with razor-sharp teeth."
msgstr "一具被未知品种植物严重侵染的尸体。尽管其动作非常僵硬，但嘴部已发生变异，占据了整个面部，边缘布满锋利的牙齿。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid "BL9 ivy zombie brute"
msgid_plural "BL9 ivy zombie brutes"
msgstr[0] "BL9常春藤蛮兵僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 ivy zombie brute'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid ""
"A corpse with huge swollen muscles severely infested by the plant of unknown"
" variety. Although it's movement is very stiff, it's mouth has altered to an"
" extent, it occupies the entirety of it's face that's lined with razor-sharp"
" teeth."
msgstr "一具肌肉异常肿胀、被未知品种植物严重侵染的尸体。尽管其动作非常僵硬，但嘴部已发生变异，占据了整个面部，边缘布满锋利的牙齿。"

#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid "BL9 ivy bulb zombie"
msgid_plural "BL9 ivy bulb zombies"
msgstr[0] "BL9常春藤球茎僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'BL9 ivy bulb zombie'}
#: .\Monsters\BL9monsters\wild_flora_fauna.json
msgid ""
"A corpse severely infested by the plant of unknown variety. Although it's "
"movement is very stiff, it's body burst into an armored bulb sort of a "
"protrusion that occupies the upper part of it entirely, the inside of the "
"bulb is horribly lined with razor-sharp teeth."
msgstr "一具被未知品种植物严重侵染的尸体。尽管其动作非常僵硬，但其身体爆裂出一个装甲球茎状的突起，完全占据了上半身，球茎内部可怕地布满锋利的牙齿。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Welcome to BL9 Safety Base, survivor of hope in life, you don't mind if I "
"call you like this? All systems are online, Energy Shield works exactly as "
"my masters, as we have all, hoped for, thanks to your work! If inhabitants "
"decide to go outside, shield will be deactivated for a split second then "
"turned on again. If inhabitants decide to go back here, scanners, installed "
"near entrance, will scan them, if they are former inhabitants, inhabitants "
"will be able to go back here, shield will be deactivated for split second "
"then turned back on again. My masters ordered me to advise you to make this "
"your permanent, safe home here. Make a family, bring your love here, have "
"children, adopt children, live as a civilization hopefully as well"
msgstr ""
"欢迎来到BL9安全基地，生命的希望幸存者，你不介意我这样称呼你吧？所有系统均已上线，能量护盾正如我的主人们，以及我们所有人所期望的那样正常工作，这要感谢你的努力！如果居民决定外出，护盾会瞬间关闭然后重新启动。如果居民决定返回这里，安装在入口附近的扫描仪会扫描他们，如果他们是前居民，居民将能够返回，护盾会瞬间关闭然后重新启动。我的主人们命令我建议你将这里作为你永久的、安全的家园。组建家庭，将你的爱人带到这里，生儿育女，收养孩子，也希望你能像文明社会一样生活。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Welcome to BL9 Safety Base, I am a control Android. We are one system of "
"multiple control machines connected via a network. We are built with a "
"purpose to ensure safe work of all systems in BL9 Safety Bases. If you are "
"new here, I suggest you to access my storage system with intel along with "
"journals in order to learn as much information as possible about essentially"
" everything related to BL9, which has been collected by my masters, this is "
"a must. If you are already experienced, know what our main goals are, feel "
"free to ask me questions that you have"
msgstr ""
"欢迎来到BL9安全基地，我是控制型安卓机器人。我们是一个由多台控制机器通过网络连接组成的系统。我们的建造目的是确保BL9安全基地内所有系统的安全工作。如果你是初来乍到，我建议你访问我的存储系统，里面包含情报和日志，以便尽可能多地了解与BL9相关的一切信息，这些信息由我的主人们收集，这是必须的。如果你已经经验丰富，知道我们的主要目标是什么，请随时向我提问。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "I want to talk about Shield Generator"
msgstr "我想谈谈护盾发生器。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is the purpose of these BL9 Safety Bases?"
msgstr "这些BL9安全基地的目的是什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"[LORE] You have mentioned storage system of yours with intel along with "
"journals to read. Can you show them to me?"
msgstr "[背景故事] 你提到过你存储系统里有情报和日志可以阅读。能给我看看吗？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"[MISSIONS] I have been told that you will offer me further instructions. Do "
"you have any missions for me to do?"
msgstr "[任务] 我被告知你会给我进一步的指示。你有什么任务要交给我做吗？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "Who is this man in Leisure Center?"
msgstr "休闲中心里的这个人是谁？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Why are there these hostile armed patrols roaming around? There are even "
"aliens? How can I fight them?"
msgstr "为什么周围有这些敌对的武装巡逻队？甚至还有外星人？我该怎么对付他们？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json .\NPC\BL9_trader.json .\NPC\NPC_missions.json
msgid "[GOODBYE]"
msgstr "[告别]"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "Have you managed to acquire Shield Generator?"
msgstr "你成功获得护盾发生器了吗？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"I have managed to acquire Shield Generator, activate Shield Generator now"
msgstr "我已经成功获得护盾发生器，现在激活护盾发生器。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "I have not acquired Shield Generator yet"
msgstr "我还没有获得护盾发生器。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json .\NPC\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Can I talk to you about something else?"
msgstr "我能和你谈谈别的吗？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate Radio Call. You can hear me? I am the creator of this Shield "
"Generator that you have helped us to activate! You have managed to do this! "
"Also, these structures that belong to 'Alliance', some of which you have "
"cleared, have a lot of remaining tech for our scavengers teams to salvage. "
"This means that not only your BL9 Safety Base is a beacon of hope for life "
"now, but also our own structures! We can actually restore civilization, "
"restore humanity now! Power cells in these generators will work for a very "
"long time, decades, if not for a century essentially. Not even mentioning "
"remaining tech that 'Alliance' has, which is essentially an endless supply "
"of power cells for us! This BL9 Safety Base now belongs to you, survivor of "
"hope in life, you can live, love, try to procreate, build a family in your "
"own really safe shelter! This is what we will also try to do! May God keep "
"you, keep all of us healthy, safe, bring you, bring all of us luck hopefully"
" as well"
msgstr ""
"发起无线电呼叫。你能听到我吗？我就是你帮助我们激活的这个护盾发生器的创造者！你成功做到了！另外，那些属于‘联盟’的建筑，其中一些你已清理，还留有许多技术可供我们的搜刮队回收。这意味着，不仅你的BL9安全基地现在是生命的希望灯塔，我们自己的建筑也是！我们现在真的可以恢复文明，恢复人类了！这些发生器里的能量电池将工作很长时间，几十年，甚至可能长达一个世纪。更不用说‘联盟’留下的技术，这基本上为我们提供了无尽的能量电池供应！这个BL9安全基地现在属于你了，生命的希望幸存者，你可以在你自己真正安全的庇护所里生活、相爱、尝试繁衍、组建家庭！这也是我们将努力去做的！愿上帝保佑你，保佑我们所有人健康、平安，也愿上帝带给你，带给我们所有人好运。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "Same to you"
msgstr "你也一样。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"That's okay, do it at your own pace, try to follow order of locations, "
"stated in missions, also try to read intel along with journals hopefully as "
"well"
msgstr "没关系，按照你自己的节奏来，尽量遵循任务中说明的地点顺序，也希望你能阅读情报和日志。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"The sole purpose of BL9 Safety Bases is to make safe areas for people to "
"live, work, love, procreate, make families, have children, adopt children, "
"live as a civilization in. Thanks to your work, we have an active Energy "
"Shield now, which makes an already relatively safe area a beacon of hope, "
"civilization for people, for you also. My masters advise you to make this "
"your permanent, safe home here. Try to do things that I have listed. Try to "
"do what, in the past, was a luxury, but thanks to your work now is "
"accessible, is what all people should strive for hopefully. Just try to help"
" me with cleaning, alright? Humans along with 'Alliance' are not that "
"different. Both make a lot of mess when they eat or have a sexual "
"intercourse. Don't ask me how I know this"
msgstr ""
"BL9安全基地的唯一宗旨是为人们提供安全区域，以便生活、工作、相爱、繁衍、组建家庭、生育子女、收养子女，作为文明社会而存在。多亏了你的努力，我们现在拥有了活跃的能量护盾，这使得原本相对安全的区域成为人类文明希望的灯塔，对你也是如此。我的主人们建议你将此地作为永久安全的家园。尝试完成我所列举的事项。尝试去做那些在过去曾是奢侈，但如今因你的工作而触手可及的事情，这应是所有人努力追求的目标。只需尽力帮我打扫卫生，好吗？人类与'联盟'并无太大不同。两者在进食或交配时都会弄得一团糟。别问我怎么知道这些的。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"The sole purpose of BL9 Safety Bases is to make safe areas for people to "
"live, work, love, procreate, make families, have children, adopt children, "
"live as a civilization in. Even without active Energy Shield, these are "
"still relatively safe areas to live in, try to do things that I have listed."
" However, to ensure protection from all living horrors of Cataclysm, we need"
" actually to have active Energy Shield hopefully. You can still try to do "
"things from this list whenever you want to. Just try to help me with "
"cleaning, alright? Humans along with 'Alliance' are not that different. Both"
" make a lot of mess when they eat or have a sexual intercourse. Don't ask me"
" how I know this"
msgstr ""
"BL9安全基地的唯一宗旨是为人们提供安全区域，以便生活、工作、相爱、繁衍、组建家庭、生育子女、收养子女，作为文明社会而存在。即使没有活跃的能量护盾，这些区域仍是相对安全的居住地，尝试完成我所列举的事项。然而，为确保免受大灾变中所有活体恐怖的侵害，我们实际上需要拥有活跃的能量护盾。你仍可随时尝试完成此列表中的事项。只需尽力帮我打扫卫生，好吗？人类与'联盟'并无太大不同。两者在进食或交配时都会弄得一团糟。别问我怎么知道这些的。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Good luck, feel free to come back here, either alone or with your friends, "
"or your love, whenever you want to, survivor"
msgstr "祝你好运，幸存者，随时欢迎回来，无论是独自一人还是与朋友或爱人一起。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json .\NPC\BL9_trader.json .\NPC\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Thanks"
msgstr "谢谢。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Sure thing! This system is pretty exquisite. Each intel along with journal "
"is categorized carefully so that you can access your chosen category for you"
" to look at it's contents to ask me questions"
msgstr "当然！这个系统相当精致。每份情报与日志都经过仔细分类，以便你访问所选类别，查看其内容并向我提问。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "[BL9 and secret human organizations intel]"
msgstr "[BL9与秘密人类组织情报]"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "[Alien fauna and advanced aliens civilizations intel]"
msgstr "[外星动植物与先进外星文明情报]"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "[Humans and secret human organizations journals]"
msgstr "[人类与秘密人类组织日志]"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "[Translated advanced alien civilizations journals]"
msgstr "[已翻译的先进外星文明日志]"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "[Legendary humans journals]"
msgstr "[传奇人类日志]"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What questions do you have about BL9 and secret organizations intel?"
msgstr "关于BL9与秘密组织情报，你有什么问题？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is BL9?"
msgstr "BL9是什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What kind of an organization do you represent?"
msgstr "你代表的是哪种组织？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is the main purpose of your organization's existence?"
msgstr "你组织存在的主要目的是什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Who are these bloodthirsty evil cultists roaming on the streets? Where do "
"they reside in general?"
msgstr "那些在街上游荡的嗜血邪恶教徒是谁？他们通常藏身何处？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Who are these hostile pretentious military looking mercenaries roaming on "
"the streets? Where do they reside in general?"
msgstr "那些在街上游荡的敌对、装腔作势的军事风格雇佣兵是谁？他们通常藏身何处？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "How did BL9 get to Earth? Some kind of meteorites impact sites?"
msgstr "BL9是如何来到地球的？是某种陨石撞击点吗？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Do these meteorites impact sites have something to do with obsession of "
"these extremists with regards to exploring, hunting for BL9?"
msgstr "这些陨石撞击点是否与那些极端分子对探索、猎取BL9的痴迷有关？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. It's a sentient, very intelligent alien symbiote that has managed to appear on Earth via space warp gate, portals on Earth, fallen meteorites as well. It's only way of survival is via finding a host, causing a symbiosis. Symbiosis, depending on many factors, can vary. To list them, these can be BL9's attitude towards it's hosts, type of BL9 it is, whether BL9's structure was artificially changed somehow.\n"
" \n"
"    Symbiosis can be benign and even protective, granting it's host inhumane powers, protection. It can also lead to all kinds of incredible mutations that can turn hosts feral, mad yet obedient at the same time pretty much. Latter is something that 'THEY' often utilize to create an army of mindless obedient mutants as well"
msgstr ""
"启动花式阅读模式。它是一种有感知、高度智能的外星共生体，通过空间扭曲门、地球上的传送门以及坠落的陨石来到地球。它唯一的生存方式是寻找宿主，建立共生关系。共生关系根据多种因素而变化。列举如下：BL9对其宿主的态度、BL9的类型、BL9的结构是否被人工改变。\n"
"\n"
"    共生可以是良性的甚至具有保护性，赋予宿主非人的力量与防护。也可能导致各种不可思议的突变，使宿主变得野蛮、疯狂却又同时相当顺从。后者常被'他们'利用来创建一支无脑顺从的突变体军队。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. We represent a secret organization that has existed pre-Cataclysm as well. Our current goals are researching peculiar alien microorganisms, minerals, gases and liquids. Also, no doubt, one of our top priorities is finding efficient ways to survive, restore our former main hub's glory. A dream of ours to make some kind of a safe place for people to live, work, love each other in as well.\n"
" \n"
"    It will take a lot of time, especially with fending off these invaders, dealing with other microorganisms, like Mycus, Triffids, and experimenting on mutations to possibly find a way to counter The Blob somehow"
msgstr ""
"启动花式阅读模式。我们代表一个在大灾变前就已存在的秘密组织。我们当前的目标是研究奇特的外星微生物、矿物、气体和液体。同时，毫无疑问，我们的首要任务之一是寻找有效的生存方式，恢复我们昔日主枢纽的荣光。我们的梦想是为人们创造一个安全的地方，以便生活、工作、相爱。\n"
"\n"
"    这将需要大量时间，尤其是在抵御这些入侵者、处理其他微生物如真菌、三裂植物，以及进行突变实验以可能找到某种对抗'团块'的方法方面。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. We specialize in research in terms of learning about inner structure and uses of peculiar alien microorganisms, minerals, gases and liquids. This also includes The Blob, Mycus, Triffids. Newest one that we research more diligently is BL9, because out of all of them, BL9 is the most unique, flexible. Based on initial experiments, it is pretty easy to affect and alter, change it's structure.\n"
" \n"
"    It's unique abilities can lead to horrible mutations or possibly some kind of a cure or protection from other microorganisms as well"
msgstr ""
"启动花式阅读模式。我们专注于研究奇特外星微生物、矿物、气体和液体的内部结构与用途。这包括'团块'、真菌、三裂植物。我们最新且更深入研究的是BL9，因为在所有微生物中，BL9是最独特、最灵活的。基于初步实验，它相当容易影响和改变其结构。\n"
"\n"
"    其独特能力可能导致可怕的突变，或可能提供某种治愈或防护其他微生物的方法。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Hmm, 'Cult' is a moderately spread occult group led by this strange man, living in a gigantic Castle with essentially a countless amount of servants, in isolation. They practice horrible occult beliefs with human sacrifices, cleansing one's blood with barely edible and strange things and drugs that they produce themselves. Based on various rumors, they are even practicing cannibalism, but not exactly sure, to be honest.\n"
" \n"
"    They have allied with 'THEM' in exchange for more advanced BL9 samples that Castlelan has already come across and started to forcefully infuse his servants with. They believe that BL9 is a blood or remnant of some sorts of their chaotic war deity, valuable sign for them"
msgstr ""
"启动花式阅读模式。嗯，'教派'是一个由这位怪人领导的中等规模的邪教团体，居住在一座巨大的城堡中，拥有几乎无数的仆人，与世隔绝。他们奉行可怕的邪教信仰，进行人祭，用几乎不可食用且奇怪的东西以及他们自制的药物来净化血液。根据各种传闻，他们甚至实行食人，但老实说，不太确定。\n"
"\n"
"    他们与'他们'结盟，以换取更先进的BL9样本，这些样本城堡领主已经遇到并开始强行注入其仆人体内。他们认为BL9是某种混沌战争之神的血液或遗物，对他们来说是宝贵的象征。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Hmm, 'THEY' is a hostile organization to us. "
"They utilize The Blob, Mycus, Triffids, BL9 in horrendous and inhumane ways."
" Their main goal is to create an army of obedient mutants, with an intention"
" of conquering local areas first and then entire Earth, creating a 'New "
"Order' of some sorts. They strive to have all civilians, mutants infused "
"with BL9, for them to be entirely obedient to their leader and mastermind of"
" some sorts. Whoever this person is, that's a madman in reality pretty much"
msgstr ""
"启动花式阅读模式。嗯，'他们'是一个对我们怀有敌意的组织。他们以可怕且不人道的方式利用'团块'、真菌、三裂植物和BL9。他们的主要目标是创建一支顺从的突变体军队，意图先征服当地区域，然后征服整个地球，建立某种'新秩序'。他们努力让所有平民、突变体都注入BL9，以便完全服从他们的领袖和某种主谋。无论此人是谁，实际上都是个疯子。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Biomes, so we call these areas of meteorites' impact. Apparently, not only BL9 but other various alien microorganisms, minerals, liquids and gases have entered soils and Earth's atmosphere in places of impact as well. This resulted in pollutions and creation of strangely colored biomes. A lot of valuable materials can be salvaged from there.\n"
" \n"
"    However, we are not the only ones who seek them and these places are quite infested with peculiar creatures as well"
msgstr ""
"启动花式阅读模式。生物群落，我们如此称呼这些陨石撞击区域。显然，不仅BL9，其他各种外星微生物、矿物、液体和气体也进入了撞击点的土壤和地球大气层。这导致了污染并形成了颜色奇特的生物群落。许多有价值的材料可以从那里回收。\n"
"\n"
"    然而，我们并非唯一寻求这些材料的人，这些地方也充斥着奇特的生物。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Well, there are former facilities that we know about with alien fauna along with mutants, however there are also lesser known much more dangerous cave biomes systems hidden beneath fortification towers of 'True Superiors' who seem to be friendly not only with Cult along with 'THEM' but also with 'Alliance' as well. All kinds of dangerous alien creatures inhabit each of them. These include mutated animal types, insectoids, weird mutated creatures, soldiers of 'True Superiors', advanced alien civilizations as well.\n"
" \n"
"    Now, most dangerous ones are advanced aliens' mobile bases, where we should not venture until we are strong enough physically, in terms of our equipment, weapons to handle these pillagers. 'Alliance', that's how they call themselves"
msgstr ""
"启动花式阅读模式。嗯，我们知道一些前设施，里面有外星动植物和突变体，但也有更隐蔽、更危险的洞穴生物群落系统，隐藏在'真正上位者'的防御塔下，他们似乎不仅与教派和'他们'友好，还与'联盟'友好。各种危险的外星生物栖息于其中。包括突变动物类型、昆虫类、奇怪的突变生物、'真正上位者'的士兵以及先进外星文明。\n"
"\n"
"    现在，最危险的是先进外星人的移动基地，在我们身体足够强壮、装备武器足以应对这些掠夺者之前，不应冒险进入。'联盟'，他们如此自称。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"What questions do you have about alien fauna and advanced civilizations "
"intel?"
msgstr "关于外星动植物与先进文明情报，你有什么问题？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is 'Alliance'? What makes them so powerful?"
msgstr "'联盟'是什么？是什么让他们如此强大？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"You have mentioned alien fauna. What are Inhravtidius aliens? How do they "
"look like?"
msgstr "你提到了外星动植物。Inhravtidius外星人是什么？他们长什么样？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"You have mentioned alien fauna. What are Yengnutrium aliens? How do they "
"look like?"
msgstr "你提到了外星动植物。Yengnutrium外星人是什么？他们长什么样？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"You have mentioned alien fauna. What are Ulniviunite aliens? How do they "
"look like?"
msgstr "你提到了外星动植物。Ulniviunite外星人是什么？他们长什么样？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"You have mentioned alien fauna. What are Ezrondium aliens? How do they look "
"like?"
msgstr "你提到了外星动物群。Ezrondium外星人是什么？它们长什么样？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Can you explain 'Alliance' presence along with their motives here on our "
"planet? What do they want to do on Earth?"
msgstr "你能解释一下'联盟'在我们星球上的存在以及他们的动机吗？他们想在地球上做什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"How did 'Alliance' become so advanced that they are considered pillagers of "
"struggling planets?"
msgstr "'联盟'是如何变得如此先进，以至于被认为是挣扎星球的掠夺者？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is the main specialization of Arganoides in general?"
msgstr "Arganoides的主要专长是什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is the main specialization of Wanzeltiums in general?"
msgstr "Wanzeltiums的主要专长是什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is the main specialization of Davranides in general?"
msgstr "Davranides的主要专长是什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid "What is the main specialization of Saldeniums in general?"
msgstr "Saldeniums的主要专长是什么？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"What does 'Alliance' want to do with BL9 in general? Why do they consider "
"BL9 important?"
msgstr "'联盟'想对BL9做什么？为什么他们认为BL9很重要？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. They call themselves 'Alliance', an alien "
"alliance of Earth pillagers that consists of 4 alien tribes from different "
"planets. Each is a former savage, but they have managed to turn into actual "
"advanced alien civilizations with the help of unique energy sources on their"
" planets. Essentially they have learned to form materials out of this "
"energy. This includes advanced craft materials, a type of a fuel. They have "
"even learned to use it as weapons, conjuring energy mass to use against "
"their enemies. They are Arganoides, Wanzeltiums, Davranides, Saldeniums as "
"well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。他们自称'联盟'，一个由来自不同星球的4个外星部落组成的地球掠夺者外星联盟。每个部落都曾是野蛮人，但借助各自星球上的独特能源，他们成功转变为真正先进的外星文明。本质上，他们学会了利用这种能量制造材料。这包括先进的工艺材料，一种燃料。他们甚至学会了将其用作武器，召唤能量团攻击敌人。他们是Arganoides、Wanzeltiums、Davranides、Saldeniums。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. These alien species are native to a beautiful water planet of Davranides. Inhravtidius resemble crustacean-like creatures, they breed and live in caves, corrals of this planet. They have a thick curved carapace, 2 antennas protruding from their heads, multiple eyes, quickly moving tiny legs and 2 sharp and spiked pincers.\n"
" \n"
"    Obviously, Davranides have brought them here. Possibly for using them as experimental subjects for infusing with BL9, since it is the main reason 'Alliance' is here. We must approach them carefully. If they are infused with BL9 then many of them must have mutated as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。这些外星物种原产于Davranides美丽的海洋星球。Inhravtidius类似甲壳类生物，它们在这个星球的洞穴、珊瑚中繁殖和生活。它们有厚而弯曲的甲壳，头部伸出2根触角，多只眼睛，快速移动的小腿和2只尖锐带刺的钳子。\n"
"\n"
"显然，Davranides把它们带到了这里。可能是为了将它们用作注入BL9的实验对象，因为这是'联盟'在此的主要原因。我们必须小心接近它们。如果它们被注入了BL9，那么其中许多肯定也发生了变异。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. These alien species are native to a swamp-like shrouded by glowing purple fog of some sorts planet of Arganoides. Yengnutrium are insectoids, resembling a strange mix of mantises and locusts, they breed and live in dryer underground cave systems of this planet. They have an elongated body, 2 antennas protruding from their heads, multiple eyes, many of them may have wings and 2 sharp serrated claws.\n"
" \n"
"    Obviously, Arganoides have brought them here. Possibly for using them as experimental subjects for infusing with BL9, since it is the main reason 'Alliance' is here. We must approach them carefully. If they are infused with BL9 then many of them must have mutated as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。这些外星物种原产于Arganoides的沼泽般、笼罩着某种发光紫色雾气的星球。Yengnutrium是昆虫类，类似螳螂和蝗虫的奇怪混合体，它们在这个星球较干燥的地下洞穴系统中繁殖和生活。它们有细长的身体，头部伸出2根触角，多只眼睛，许多可能有翅膀和2只尖锐锯齿状的爪子。\n"
"\n"
"显然，Arganoides把它们带到了这里。可能是为了将它们用作注入BL9的实验对象，因为这是'联盟'在此的主要原因。我们必须小心接近它们。如果它们被注入了BL9，那么其中许多肯定也发生了变异。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. These alien species are native to a beautiful and dense jungle-like wildforests planet of Wanzeltiums. Ulniviunite are pangolin-like creatures, they breed and live in sandy cave areas located on shores of this planet. They have a body covered with slime, coated thick and durable scales, underbelly and tail grotesquely fleshy and slimy, lamprey-type mouth with a menacingly looking set of teeth, long anteater-like tongue along with incredibly thick and sturdy claws on the end of it's limbs.\n"
" \n"
"    Obviously, Wanzeltiums have brought them here. Possibly for using them as experimental subjects for infusing with BL9, since it is the main reason 'Alliance' is here. We must approach them carefully. If they are infused with BL9 then many of them must have mutated as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。这些外星物种原产于Wanzeltiums美丽茂密的丛林般野生森林星球。Ulniviunite是穿山甲类生物，它们在这个星球海岸边的沙质洞穴区域繁殖和生活。它们的身体覆盖着黏液，披着厚实耐用的鳞片，腹部和尾巴 grotesquely fleshy and slimy，七鳃鳗型的嘴配有一副狰狞的牙齿，长如食蚁兽的舌头，以及四肢末端极其粗壮坚固的爪子。\n"
"\n"
"显然，Wanzeltiums把它们带到了这里。可能是为了将它们用作注入BL9的实验对象，因为这是'联盟'在此的主要原因。我们必须小心接近它们。如果它们被注入了BL9，那么其中许多肯定也发生了变异。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. These alien species are native to a volcanic canyons barren wasteland-like planet of Saldeniums. Ezrondium are arachnides resembling gigantic spiders, they breed and live in sandy cave areas located on shores of this planet. They have an enormous body from belly of which emerges a small worm-like protrusion, incredibly sharp and deadly looking elongated legs.\n"
" \n"
"    Obviously, Saldeniums have brought them here. Possibly for using them as experimental subjects for infusing with BL9, since it is the main reason 'Alliance' is here. We must approach them carefully. If they are infused with BL9 then many of them must have mutated as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。这些外星物种原产于Saldeniums的火山峡谷荒原般星球。Ezrondium是类似巨型蜘蛛的蛛形纲生物，它们在这个星球海岸边的沙质洞穴区域繁殖和生活。它们有巨大的身体，腹部伸出一个蠕虫状的小突起，极其尖锐且致命的长腿。\n"
"\n"
"显然，Saldeniums把它们带到了这里。可能是为了将它们用作注入BL9的实验对象，因为这是'联盟'在此的主要原因。我们必须小心接近它们。如果它们被注入了BL9，那么其中许多肯定也发生了变异。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. It's an alliance of alien invaders. These are 3 of them, Arganoides, Wanzeltiums, Davranides alien civilizations. There was one more, Saldeniums alien civilization, but they were too bloodthirsty to build mutually beneficial relations with someone so they were disposed of thanks to combined effort of other alien invaders alliance members which are definitely much more civilized. Their main reason of allying is supporting each other for successful survival on ravaged Earth, considering presence of all these hostile creatures here. Most important thing to them is BL9, they are obsessed with it, they seek it diligently.\n"
" \n"
"    They've learned, thanks to Davranides' research, that alien symbiotes are capable of granting their hosts incredible abilities. They've learned that BL9 is incredibly advanced, capable of being greatly modified. They've somehow learned that it is present on Earth, likely with their spy drones or portal spy teams, this is why they're here as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。这是一个外星入侵者联盟。其中有三个，Arganoides、Wanzeltiums、Davranides外星文明。还有一个，Saldeniums外星文明，但他们过于嗜血，无法与任何人建立互利关系，因此被其他外星入侵者联盟成员联手清除，这些成员无疑文明得多。他们结盟的主要原因是相互支持，以便在被蹂躏的地球上成功生存，考虑到这里所有敌对生物的存在。对他们最重要的是BL9，他们对此着迷，孜孜不倦地寻找它。\n"
"\n"
"通过Davranides的研究，他们了解到外星共生体能够赋予宿主不可思议的能力。他们了解到BL9极其先进，能够被大幅改造。他们不知何故得知它存在于地球上，可能是通过间谍无人机或传送间谍小队，这也是他们来到这里的原因。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Honestly, it's nowhere to be found when they've created their civilizations. Still, presence of hostile fauna, pretty harsh environmental conditions, all of this kind of makes an assumption that this would have hindered their progress sufficiently. What gave them so much strength is that they've found a unique source of energy on each of their planets.\n"
" \n"
"    In main journal we have already explained how they've used it to evolve from savages. However, it also boosts their physical capabilities. Crystalline glow that they have is due to their high consumption of this energy. They have become addicted to it, even with all advancements of theirs, they run out of this energy supply. They seek BL9 for this reason as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。老实说，在他们创建文明时，这根本找不到。然而，敌对动物群的存在，相当恶劣的环境条件，所有这些都让人推测这会严重阻碍他们的进步。给予他们如此强大力量的是他们在各自星球上发现了一种独特的能源。\n"
"\n"
"在主日志中，我们已经解释了他们是怎样利用它从野蛮人进化而来的。然而，它也增强了他们的身体能力。他们身上的晶体光芒是由于他们大量消耗这种能量。他们对此上瘾了，即使拥有所有进步，他们的这种能源供应也会耗尽。他们也因此寻找BL9。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Well, Arganoides are adventurers, explorers, mercenaries in general. They are native to a swamp-like shrouded by purple fog of some sorts planet. They are proficient at tracking, searching for anything that they consider valuable, it is their greatest skill.\n"
" \n"
"    They are tall graceful humanoid beings, emitting bright purple crystalline light. It's head resembles a water shaped droplet with hair-like long tentacles growing out of it, it has elongated eyes as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。嗯，Arganoides通常是冒险家、探索者、雇佣兵。他们原产于一个沼泽般、笼罩着某种紫色雾气的星球。他们擅长追踪、寻找任何他们认为有价值的东西，这是他们最伟大的技能。\n"
"\n"
"他们是高大优雅的人形生物，发出明亮的紫色晶体光芒。头部类似水滴形状，长出发丝般的长触手，还有细长的眼睛。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Well, Wanzeltiums are builders, engineers, craftsmen in general. They are native to a beautiful and dense jungle-like wildforests planet. They are masters of creating magnificent structures, ingeniously made tech, sturdy and durable armor along with strong weapons, it is their greatest skill.\n"
" \n"
"    They are over 5'8 feet tall reptile-like humanoids, emitting a bright green crystalline light. It has a reptilian-humanoid head having a greatly widened forehead covered with multiple thick skin lines, multiple hair-like spiky protrusions coming out of the back and sides of it's head, having wide eyes as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。嗯，Wanzeltiums通常是建造者、工程师、工匠。他们原产于一个美丽茂密的丛林般野生森林星球。他们是创造宏伟结构、巧妙制造技术、坚固耐用盔甲以及强大武器的大师，这是他们最伟大的技能。\n"
"\n"
"他们是超过5英尺8英寸（约1.73米）高的爬虫类人形生物，发出明亮的绿色晶体光芒。他们有爬虫类人形头部，前额大大加宽，覆盖着多条厚皮肤皱纹，后脑和两侧伸出多根发丝般的尖刺突起，还有宽大的眼睛。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Well, Davranides are scientists, researchers, very professional keepers of scientific knowledge in general. They are native to a beautiful water planet. They research microorganisms, splice them, produce drugs, experiment with mutagens, symbiotes, all of this is something that they are very skilled at.\n"
" \n"
"    They are average height smooth-skinned amphibian-like humanoids, emitting a bright azure-blue crystalline light. It has an elongated cranium with eyes that protrude from each side of it's head on short stalks, they often have a calculating gaze as well"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。嗯，Davranides通常是科学家、研究员、非常专业的科学知识守护者。他们原产于一个美丽的海洋星球。他们研究微生物，拼接它们，生产药物，实验诱变剂、共生体，所有这些他们都非常擅长。\n"
"\n"
"他们是中等身高、皮肤光滑的两栖类人形生物，发出明亮的天蓝色晶体光芒。他们有细长的头骨，眼睛从头部两侧的短柄上突出，通常还有算计的目光。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Well, Saldeniums are incredibly strong warriors, hunters, mercenaries in general. They are native to a volcanic barren wasteland-like planet. On their planet they wage wars, conquer tribes, hunt animals. In space they hunt people in cases of mercenaries, teach other combat, all of this is something that they are very proficient at.\n"
" \n"
"    Because of their savage ways, upon providing combat training to allies of theirs which was the main reason of them being accepted in first place, thanks to support of Arganoides along with pragmatism of Wanzeltiums along with devious ways of Davranides civilizations, they have been expelled from their alliance justly. They evidently objected, but having taught others everything, having no industry, having no less savage, more practical merits of their own, they've become a liability, thrown back to their own planet"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。嗯，Saldeniums通常是极其强大的战士、猎人、雇佣兵。他们原产于一个火山荒原般星球。在他们的星球上，他们发动战争，征服部落，狩猎动物。在太空中，作为雇佣兵，他们猎杀人类，教授他人战斗，所有这些他们都非常精通。\n"
"\n"
"由于他们的野蛮方式，在向盟友提供战斗训练后（这是他们最初被接纳的主要原因），在Arganoides的支持、Wanzeltiums的务实以及Davranides文明的狡诈手段下，他们被公正地驱逐出联盟。他们显然反对，但在教会了别人一切、没有工业、没有更少野蛮、更实际的自身优点后，他们成了累赘，被扔回了自己的星球。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. Honestly, Arganoides are interested mainly in using it as a high quality fuel for their spaceships, more efficient locating tech for acquiring rare valuable items. Wanzeltiums want to use it for creating more durable and unique building materials, improving their existing tech and weapons via infusing it with BL9.\n"
" \n"
"    Davranides crave to significantly advance their existent mutation, splicing research in an attempt to make their race genetically superior via their own efforts"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。老实说，Arganoides主要感兴趣的是将其用作他们宇宙飞船的高质量燃料，以及更高效的定位技术来获取稀有贵重物品。Wanzeltiums想用它来创造更耐用和独特的建筑材料，通过注入BL9来改进他们现有的技术和武器。\n"
"\n"
"Davranides渴望通过他们自己的努力，显著推进他们现有的突变和拼接研究，试图使他们的种族在基因上更优越。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Which of humans and human organizations journals do you want me to read?"
msgstr "你想让我阅读哪类人类或人类组织的日志？"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"I want you to read journal which belongs to one of your organization's "
"agents"
msgstr "我想让你阅读属于你们组织某位特工的日志"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"I want you to read first journal which belongs to this 'Subject5' anonymous "
"supporter of your organization I think"
msgstr "我想让你阅读第一本日志，它属于你们组织的匿名支持者'Subject5'，我认为"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"I want you to read second journal which belongs to this 'Subject5' anonymous"
" supporter of your organization I think"
msgstr "我想让你阅读第二本日志，它属于你们组织的匿名支持者'Subject5'，我认为"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"I want you to read journal which belongs to one of these obsessed cultists"
msgstr "我想让你阅读属于这些狂热邪教徒之一的日志"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"I want you to read journal which belongs to one of these scheming "
"mercenaries"
msgstr "我想让你阅读属于这些阴谋雇佣兵之一的日志"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. I am an agent working on one of the remnants of many secret organizations that existed before Cataclysm. I was born in one of it's main hidden facilities, my father was a retired military officer who was hired as a mercenary and worked long for this organization.\n"
" \n"
"    Obviously, such organizations had and many still have many hidden facilities, vaults, many different structures, an unbelievable amount of resources to feed and supply multiple generations' of survivors and it's agents' offspring.\n"
" \n"
"    For many years I've been training diligently to become not just a survivor and a scavenger - but an agent who can search and scavenge for rare resources as well along with the basic ones. However, our own leader betrayed us, selling us to 'THEM', hoping to be one of 'THEIR' allies in New World that 'THEY' want to build.\n"
" \n"
"    'THEY' have killed, abducted many of our people, but many of us have also managed to escape. We've made secret BL9 research, safety bases thanks to Ulysses along with many of our scientists who believe that we can modify it to be safe, beneficial even to use for equipment or even drugs. I try to do my best to strive if not for flourishment but at the very least continued existence along with survival of our organization, my people..."
msgstr ""
"启动幻想阅读模式。我是一名特工，为大灾变前存在的众多秘密组织的残余势力之一工作。我出生在其主要隐藏设施之一，父亲是退役军官，受雇为雇佣兵，长期为该组织效力。\n"
"\n"
"显然，这类组织过去拥有、许多至今仍保有许多隐藏设施、避难所、各式建筑，以及难以置信的资源，足以供养和供应多代幸存者及其特工后代。\n"
"\n"
"多年来我刻苦训练，不仅为了成为幸存者和拾荒者——更要成为能搜寻稀有资源与基础物资的特工。然而，我们的领袖背叛了我们，将我们出卖给'他们'，希望成为'他们'想要建立的新世界中'他们'的盟友。\n"
"\n"
"'他们'杀害、绑架了我们许多人，但我们中也有许多人成功逃脱。得益于尤利西斯和许多相信我们能将其改造为安全、甚至有益于装备或药物的科学家，我们建立了秘密的BL9研究安全基地。我竭尽全力奋斗，不求繁荣，至少为延续我们组织和我族人的生存……"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. I've grown in one of our organization's core centers. My father is a bright very experienced symbiotes scientist, yet he's a very kind, humane person, he wants me to be a scientist. My mother is a former scientist who mutated into a very graceful plant humanoid, retaining most of her humanity. She abandoned us, because she feared of what our own people could do to our family for having a mutant as a member of our organization. Years after, I've essentially grown indifferent to my father's work.\n"
" \n"
"    'THEY' attacked our core center, our own leader betrayed all of us. Hundreds of our people killed, kidnapped, abducted. Hundreds of mutated soldiers, vile creatures with inhumane strength and agility. Some of us escaped, like my father with some scientists, workers and our main agent. I didn't follow them. I ran to labs, I've injected myself with one of experimental symbiotes, BL9, my father has been working on it for years. Managed to use my new abilities to escape safely, alone. I search for remnants of our organization, I know they exist, I know they along with my father have survived. With this intel, journals, survivors could help me, our organization to fight our enemies successfully hopefully as well"
msgstr ""
"启动幻想阅读模式。我在我们组织的核心中心之一长大。父亲是位聪明且经验丰富的共生体科学家，但他非常善良、人道，希望我成为科学家。母亲曾是科学家，后来变异成优雅的植物人形，保留了大部分人性。她离开了我们，因为她害怕组织成员会因家庭中有突变体而对我们不利。多年后，我对父亲的工作已基本漠不关心。\n"
"\n"
"'他们'袭击了我们的核心中心，我们自己的领袖背叛了我们所有人。数百同胞被杀、被绑架。数百名突变士兵，拥有非人力量与敏捷的邪恶生物。我们中有些人逃脱了，比如我父亲和一些科学家、工人及主要特工。我没有跟随他们。我跑进实验室，给自己注射了实验性共生体BL9——父亲已研究多年。凭借新能力，我独自安全逃脱。我搜寻组织的残余，我知道他们存在，我知道他们和我父亲都活了下来。有了这些情报、日志，幸存者或许能帮助我，帮助我们的组织成功对抗敌人"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. This Cataclysm, mutants, weird creatures, bandits, aliens, cults, really vile organizations, 'Alliance', all of this changes us with time. Survival becomes our main priority. We kill, we destroy, we don't trust anyone. Some forget what conscience is even. There is still a hope, many of these horrors or microorganisms can be used to our advantage, such as equipment based on alien technologies, creating healthy mutations or drugs based on modified microorganisms to make them benign, to fend off anything that corrupts us.\n"
" \n"
"    I don't know if we can still love or have children, but we must try, we all must try. I believe that we have a tiny bit of God's energy within us. With it we don't get entirely corrupted by vile sources, retaining our humane side. Based on this, we need to survive, to ascertain that ideas of good, hope, ethics, love will not be obsolete as well"
msgstr ""
"启动幻想阅读模式。这场大灾变、突变体、怪异生物、土匪、外星人、邪教、真正邪恶的组织、'联盟'，这一切都随时间改变着我们。生存成为首要任务。我们杀戮、破坏，不信任任何人。有些人甚至忘了良知为何物。但仍有希望，许多恐怖事物或微生物可为我们所用，比如基于外星科技的装备，创造健康突变或基于改良微生物的药物使其良性化，抵御腐蚀我们的一切。\n"
"\n"
"我不知道我们是否还能爱或生育，但我们必须尝试，所有人都必须尝试。我相信我们体内蕴藏一丝神性能量。借此我们不会完全被邪恶源头腐蚀，保留人性一面。基于此，我们需要生存，确保善良、希望、伦理、爱的理念不会过时"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. This strange liquified being, it gives inhumane powers to whoever consumes it. Our miners in mines of our Great Castlelan's Creation managed to find it. Some consumed it instantly out of curiousity they had. It killed ones who were not worthy of our Deity's magnificent blessing, but it gave incredible powers to ones worthy of it.\n"
" \n"
"    We believe this to be a blood of our Deity, a blessing given to us. These are means to mark us as worthy warriors to destroy heretics, anyone who opposes creation of New World, who disregards our beliefs, who presumes us to be madmen. We must fight fools and obstacles on our way, our vile enemies"
msgstr ""
"启动幻想阅读模式。这种奇异的液化存在，赋予饮用者非人的力量。我们伟大卡斯泰兰创世矿场的矿工发现了它。有人出于好奇当场饮用。它杀死了不配获得神明宏伟祝福者，却赐予配得者不可思议的力量。\n"
"\n"
"我们相信这是神明的血液，赐予我们的祝福。这是标记我们为合格战士的手段，去摧毁异端、任何反对新世界创造者、蔑视我们信仰、视我们为疯子的人。我们必须对抗途中的愚昧与阻碍，我们卑劣的敌人"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Initiate fancy reading mode. We are led by one of the brightest minds that exists during our times. The only way to rebuild this world is to create disciplined, fully obedient people, that will not dare to question our leadership, ranging from regular civilians to physically enhanced soldiers and even mutated amalgamations to use as our elite soldiers. With BL9 that's very much possible. These who will not bow down to us to accept us as leaders will be forced to infuse themselves with our own modified version of BL9\n"
" \n"
"    Also, based on BL9's properties, it counters The Blob, Triffids, Mycus entirely. This in addition to the fact that it's absolutely benign, hardly a weapon, but with a few tweaks, of course, it can be turned into a true weapon. With huge amounts of resources, weapons, materials, workforce including scientists and engineers, we can expand as an organization. Maybe even assert dominance across local areas. With more hosts, maybe even across entire country, possibly even across the world"
msgstr ""
"启动华丽阅读模式。我们由当代最杰出的头脑之一引领。重建这个世界的唯一途径，是培养纪律严明、绝对服从的人民，他们不敢质疑我们的领导，从普通平民到身体强化的士兵，甚至突变的融合体，都将作为我们的精英士兵。借助BL9，这完全可能实现。那些不愿臣服于我们、不接受我们领导的人，将被强制注入我们改良版的BL9。\n"
"\n"
"此外，基于BL9的特性，它能完全对抗The Blob、Triffids和Mycus。再加上它本身绝对无害，几乎算不上武器，但经过一些调整，当然可以变成真正的武器。凭借大量资源、武器、材料、劳动力（包括科学家和工程师），我们可以作为一个组织扩张。甚至可能在局部地区确立统治地位。随着宿主增多，或许能覆盖整个国家，甚至整个世界。"

#: .\NPC\BL9_Base_Android.json
msgid ""
"Which of translated advanced alien civilizations journals do you want to "
"read?"
msgstr "你想阅读哪本已翻译的先进外星文明日志？"

